divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: I was playing with my little brother outside and we heard a loud "looooooooooloooooooooolooooooooo" sound above us. It was headed south. We looked up and 4 lights zoomed past us going very fast. I ve already called local news stations, but this can t hurt. Please believe me, it was a scary sight.
